node.text:
$300 Goes To The Two Best Comments About A Supportive Partner/Friend/Family Member.
.
This Woman Here Has Shown Me What True Partnership Is!
.
Not Only Did She Leave A Career She Loved That Was Paying Her $250k A Year To Come Help Me Build! 🥰🙏🏾
.
But She Literally Puts Her Pride/Ego To The Side To Be Sure Things Get Done To Support Our Vision.
.
I’ve Witnessed Other Women & Men Expect Marriage From Their Partner, Benefits From Success & Keys To The Kingdom… Why…
.
✅ Because They Are Family
.
✅ Because They Were “There” While The Work Was Being Done.
.
✅ Because They Offered A Piece Of Ass & Looked Pretty.
.
People Are Really Delusional Out Here!
.
So I Wanted To Make This Appreciation Post For My Queen 👑
.
She Matches My Energy Like No Other!
.
She Out Works Everyone, Reps The Hell Out Of The Brand, Then Shows Up Serving All The Looks! 😍😋
.
Love You & Appreciate You Queen! @fit4thegoodlife

node.text:
I Don’t Know How NOT To Give Value, Wealth Building Strategies & The Overall Roadmap To A Successful Life.
.
Because Of That, I Don’t Clear My Schedule To Randomly Meet Up With People.
.
If You Just So Happen To Be In My Space At A Lamborghini Rally/Car Show Or Something, I May Hit You With A Little Game.
.
Other Than That, Time For Me Is My Most Precious Asset I Have.
.
And Because Of That, I Don’t Give It Away For Free.
.
If You Bought Into The Sales Pitch That Your Time Is Only Worth $10-50 A Hour, That’s Cool.
.
But Don’t Put Shit On Me! 😂

node.text:
Money Changes Peoples… ACTIONS!
.
It Doesn’t Necessarily Change The Person & Their True Self!
.
I’ve Been Wealthy Since I Was 26!
.
And Since Then I’ve Seen…
.
✅ People Who Didn’t Fuck With Me Change Up & Now They Kiss My Ass 😘 
✅ Love Ones “Lose Control” Over Me, So They Intentionally Sabotaged My Plans In Hopes Of Slowing Me Down.
✅ Family Talk Behind Your Back, When They Never Thought About You Before The Wealth Came!
.
It’s So Much More! This Is Why I Love Teaching Though!
.
Because Many Of You Are Climbing To The 6,7 & 8 Figure Range 🤑
.
And You Too Will Have Spouses, Friends, & Families Switch Up On You!
.
At The Bottom, I Always Blamed The Rich People For Being The Assholes That Switch Up(And Many Are)
.
But In Reality, It’s The Hating As Spectators That Really Change!
.
For All Of My Go Getters!
.
KEEP YOUR HEAD ON A SWIVEL & PROTECT YOUR PEACE! 🙏🏾
